  - TriggerRegisterPlayerChatEvent (preset:Player04, const:英雄模式, preset:ChatMatchTypeExact)
  - TriggerRegisterPlayerChatEvent (preset:Player05, const:英雄模式, preset:ChatMatchTypeExact)
  - TriggerRegisterPlayerChatEvent (preset:Player06, const:英雄模式, preset:ChatMatchTypeExact)
  - TriggerRegisterPlayerChatEvent (preset:Player07, const:英雄模式, preset:ChatMatchTypeExact)
  - TriggerRegisterPlayerChatEvent (preset:Player08, const:英雄模式, preset:ChatMatchTypeExact)
  - TriggerRegisterPlayerChatEvent (preset:Player09, const:英雄模式, preset:ChatMatchTypeExact)
  - TriggerRegisterPlayerChatEvent (preset:Player10, const:英雄模式, preset:ChatMatchTypeExact)
